org.promasi.core.equations
Class CalculatedEquation

java.lang.Object
  org.promasi.core.equations.CalculatedEquation
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, IEquation
public class CalculatedEquation
extends java.lang.Object
implements IEquation, java.io.Serializable

The calculated equation takes a string that represents the equation for example : x*y where x and y are the keys of the ISdObject that exist as a dependency in the _context. Generally the _equationString can take JEP expressions. The class follows the javabeans specification.

Author:
eddiefullmetal
